    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound, with a smooth-shifting transmission and an engine that runs quietly and reliably. The interior is clean and free of major wear, though you may find some minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior consistent with careful daily use. It's a dependable car that's ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
