      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle exhibits a pristine aesthetic and mechanical profile, reflective of a meticulous ownership history. Every surface remains unblemished, offering a showroom-equivalent experience for the discerning enthusiast. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the uncompromising quality of this investment-grade motorcar.",
      "price": 48900.0,
